        <p class="sectionTag">Wake up Inspired</p>
        <p class="sectionsubTag">
          Discover astonishing views of the rugged natural landscape from your
          private suite. Each room features graceful furnishings, a
          “Rolls-Royce” sleep experience by Simmons and exceptional design
          inspired by nature.Luxury at 11,000 feet is no mean feat! The increase
          in the number of tourists to Leh, including those who like to travel
          on a shoestring budget as well as those who are expense agnostic, has
          resulted in a surge in the number of luxury hotels in the area. Unlike
          popular perception, Leh can be an ideal destination for families
          looking for a unique experience with oodles of comfort thrown in. You
          can choose from some luxurious hotels such as the Ladakh Himalayan
          Retreat, Saboo Resorts, The Druk Ladakh or more. High on comfort,
          these hotels blend signature Ladakhi hospitality with modern day
          facilities.
        </p>
      </div>
